{"tid":570743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無業男Dummy機當iPhone賣 5買家中招","createTime":"2018-02-24T03:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T05:01:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2d0bda1336cebddbfb8ce43718a9dc32494c722b","tid":570743,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T03:38:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180224/20314073H\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180224%2F20314073H&d=zroh5YjMP%2FaGpZOrEiPSF5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f1664b67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180224%2F20314073H&h=ad12d16b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180224/20314073H</a><br />\n<br />\n無業男Dummy機當iPhone賣<br />\n5買家中招<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】警方偵破一宗以iPhone樣辦機（Dummy機）當真機出售的詐騙案，一名無業男子在網上交易平台以每部3,000多元出售iPhone 7 plus手機，5名市民不虞有詐在港鐵站與騙徒當面交收時，誤信騙徒以手機沒電或已包裝好由，沒有當場驗機，直至返家才發現是Dummy機，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方追查後昨晨在大埔將他拘捕，並撿獲iPhone 7 plus樣辦機、真iPhone手機及原包裝盒等證物。<br />\n<br />\n涉案被捕男子姓李（27歲），家住大埔，涉嫌與今年1月至2月發生的5宗網上買賣騙案有關，2男3女（17至28歲）損失金額約1.7萬元。警方稱，騙徒在不同網上交易平台出售二手iPhone手機，然後相約買家到不同港鐵站交收，並用原裝iPhone盒包裝的樣辦機交給事主，當事主欲驗機時，騙徒則藉口手機沒電或已包裝好，買家信以為真，沒即場驗機，直至返家才發現是不能使用的Dummy機，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n元朗警區刑事調查隊第7隊接手，聯同網絡安全及科技罪案調查科進行調查，昨晨7時30分在大埔一住宅單位拘捕姓李疑犯，並撿獲一部iPhone 7 plus的樣辦機、4部真iPhone手機、3部電腦以及大量包裝盒及包裝貼紙等。<br />\n<br />\n有資深收機人士提醒，可以靠3招識別假iPhone，包括核對買機單據序號與盒身是否相同、詳驗機盒包裝膠紙有無破損及曾被打開，以及以磁石隔著機盒作測試，另如能開機測試，最好嘗試使用App Store和Siri，若不成功即屬有詐。"},{"pid":"9a470125347339f9365d04979af6a4037317e66a","tid":570743,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T03:46:38.000Z","msg":"依家仲有人唔即場著機試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f474525134716f1aafb0a8e3a44cd88ed84de94c","tid":570743,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T03:50:09.000Z","msg":"依Ｄ 人抵死<br />\n唔試機"},{"pid":"b2bc45a7476047022d6148eddf540ffe2f5a469b","tid":570743,"uid":714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T04:46:30.000Z","msg":"先達班傻閪都識用磁石試啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02529b104f6c430e9e3ff32cc062e65d02017ca2","tid":570743,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2bc45a7476047022d6148eddf540ffe2f5a469b","tid":570743,"uid":714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T04:46:30.000Z","msg":"先達班傻閪都識用磁石試啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T04:50:15.000Z","msg":"磁石係點試 ？<br />\n<br />\n唔識<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feab30e0832f10fedb4443e12a455898b7a08013","tid":570743,"uid":714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"02529b104f6c430e9e3ff32cc062e65d02017ca2","tid":570743,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2bc45a7476047022d6148eddf540ffe2f5a469b","tid":570743,"uid":714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T04:46:30.000Z","msg":"先達班傻閪都識用磁石試啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T04:50:15.000Z","msg":"磁石係點試 ？<br />\n<br />\n唔識<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T05:01:48.000Z","msg":"如果包裝盒內有真機，只要將磁石的負極，對準盒內iPhone 7的聽筒位，磁石會受到聽筒的強大磁場影響，而直接彈開；如果將磁石放上同一位置，但完全沒有反應，那麼就大多是假機了。"}]}